风暴给佛罗里达州西海岸带去了很高的海浪，[[克利尔沃特_(佛罗里达州)|克利尔沃特海滩]]的[[风暴潮|风暴潮]]达到1.46米。海浪导致了轻度海岸侵蚀，[[布雷登顿_(佛罗里达州)|布雷登顿海滩]]有15至18米深的沙子被冲走。[[坦帕湾|坦帕湾]]沿岸区域有多条道路出现了轻微的水浸<ref name="tbwnws">{{cite report | author = McMichael | year = 2007 | title = Tropical Storm Barry Post Tropical Cyclone Report | publisher = Ruskin, Florida National Weather Service | accessdate = 2007-06-11}}</ref>，一些车辆因此被困<ref>{{cite news | author = Fox13 | year = 2007 | title = Barry leaves his calling card | accessdate = 2007-06-03}}</ref>。[[印度海岸_(佛罗里达州)|印度海岸]]有一位女性因大浪受伤后不治身亡<ref name="tbwnws" />。

全州都受到了强风吹袭，东南部沿海地区报告了时速76公里的大风<ref name="ap622">{{cite web | author = Associated Press | year = 2007 | title = Tropical Storm Barry brings rain to Florida | accessdate = 2007-09-30 | deadurl = yes | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20070930023506/http://www.dallasnews.com/sharedcontent/dws/news/nationworld/stories/060307dnnattsbarry.c156f.html | archivedate = 2007-09-30 | url = http://www.dallasnews.com/sharedcontent/dws/news/nationworld/stories/060307dnnattsbarry.c156f.html }}</ref>。大风刮倒了一些树木，导致州內出现局部停电<ref>{{cite web | author = Tiffany Pakkala | year = 2007 | title = Barry dumps 5 inches of rain on area | publisher = The St. Augustine Record | accessdate = 2014-04-12 | archivedate = 2013-11-03 | deadurl = yes | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20131103213257/http://staugustine.com/stories/060307/news_4633795.shtml | url = http://staugustine.com/stories/060307/news_4633795.shtml }}</ref>，[[希尔斯波罗县_(佛罗里达州)|希尔斯波罗县]][[非建制地区|非建制地区]]卡罗尔伍德（{{lang|en|Carrollwood}}）有一人因倒塌的树木砸中房屋而受伤<ref name="tbwnws" />。风暴还在该州南部催出了多场龙卷风，导致围栏和供电线路受损。[[迈阿密-戴德县|迈阿密-戴德县]]有约2000人可能因一场龙卷风刮断供电线路而失去电力供应<ref name="mh62" />。[[迈阿密|迈阿密]]附近的另一场龙卷风对一些树木和民宅构成破坏<ref name="abc30">{{cite web |author=''KFSN-TV'' |year=2007 |title=Tropical Storm Barry Brings Much Needed Rain To Florida |accessdate=2014-04-12 |url=http://abclocal.go.com/kfsn/story?section=news/local&id=5363314 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20121004132122/http://abclocal.go.com/kfsn/story?section=news%2Flocal&id=5363314 |deadurl=yes |archivedate=2012-10-04 }}</ref>。

==== 其他地区 ====
[[File:Tropical_Storm_Barry.jpg|left]]
乔治亚州以[[蒙哥马利县_(乔治亚州)|蒙哥马利县]]的[[芒特弗农_(乔治亚州)|芒特弗农]]降雨量最高，达到203毫米<ref name="hpcpa9" />。降水协助了消防员对抗该州南部一直延伸到佛罗里达州的严重山火，让已经连续奋战了超过一个月的数千名消防人员得到短暂的喘息空间<ref name="ap63">{{cite web | author = Associated Press | year = 2007 | title = First significant rain in weeks gives fire crews much-needed break | accessdate = 2007-09-26 | deadurl = yes | url = http://news.mywebpal.com/partners/680/public/news811591.html | archivedate = 2007-09-26 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20070926213010/http://news.mywebpal.com/partners/680/public/news811591.html }}</ref>。降雨导致了轻度水灾，[[萨凡纳|萨凡纳]]发生了几起轻微的交通事故<ref>{{cite news | author = Savannah Morning News | year = 2007 | title = Barry brings relief with 5 inches of rain | accessdate = 2007-06-03}}</ref>。强烈的阵风吹倒了一些树木，还刮断了多条供电线路，沿海报告出现了强烈的海浪<ref name="gancdc">{{cite report | author = | title = Tropical Storm Barry Event Report for Georgia (2) | year = 2007 | publisher = National Climatic Data Center | accessdate = 2008-11-25}}</ref>。[[美国东岸|美国东岸]]因这场风暴普降大雨，南卡罗莱纳州以[[哈迪维尔_(南卡罗莱纳州)|哈迪维尔]]附近降雨量最高，达到155毫米<ref name="hpcpa9" />，北卡罗莱纳州最高的则是富基瓦里纳（{{lang|en|Fuquay-Varina}}），有95毫米，[[弗吉尼亚州|弗吉尼亚州]]的彭宁顿加普（{{lang|en|Pennington Gap}}）也有95毫米<ref name="hpcpa14" />。南卡罗莱纳州还受到了强风的吹袭<ref name="gancdc" />。

巴里的温带残留给大西洋沿岸带去了强烈的阵风，南卡罗莱纳州[[查尔斯顿_(南卡罗莱纳州)|查尔斯顿]]附近达到最高的97公里时速<ref name="hpcpa7" />。北卡罗莱纳州[[克雷文县_(北卡罗莱纳州)|克雷文县]]有约200套房屋因大风刮断了一条供电线路而停电<ref>{{cite web |author=Charlie Hall |publisher=New Bern Sun Journal |year=2007 |accessdate=2012-02-25 |title=Barry causes few problems in region |archivedate=2012-02-25 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120225082428/http://www.newbernsj.com/news/sunday-34694-afternoon-rain.html |url=http://www.newbernsj.com/news/sunday-34694-afternoon-rain.html }}</ref>。北卡罗莱纳州因风暴产生的不利影响而推迟了[[东卡罗莱纳大学|东卡罗莱纳大学]]和[[西卡罗莱纳大学|西卡罗莱纳大学]]之间的一场棒球赛<ref>{{cite web | author = Bonesville.net | year = 2007 | title = Chapel Hill Regional slips in the rain | accessdate = 2014-04-12 | archivedate = 2012-02-29 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20120229184045/http://bonesville.net/Articles/OtherArticles/Bonesville/Bonesville_Baseball/2007/Regionals/060307_Rain.htm | url = http://bonesville.net/Articles/OtherArticles/Bonesville/Bonesville_Baseball/2007/Regionals/060307_Rain.htm }}</ref>。[[弗吉尼亚州|弗吉尼亚州]]因巴里的残余导致了超过60起交通事故，共有10人受伤<ref>{{cite web | author = Steve Stone and Amy Coutee | year = 2007 | title = Tropical storm's leftovers force cancellations across region | publisher = Virginia Pilot | accessdate = 2007-06-04 | url = http://hamptonroads.com/node/276471 | archivedate = 2012-10-02 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20121002081617/http://hamptonroads.com/node/276471 }}</ref>。恐怖角（{{lang|en|Cape Fear}}）近海一艘帆船因海况恶劣而不得不向[[海岸巡防队|海岸巡防队]]求救<ref>{{cite news | author = Daily Press | year = 2007 | title = Boaters off Cape Fear rescued | accessdate = 2014-04-12 | url = http://news.google.com/newspapers?nid=1454&dat=20070604&id=b8giAAAAIBAJ&sjid=_R8EAAAAIBAJ&pg=2574,1453605}}</ref>。降水还经新英格兰延伸到了[[中大西洋各州|中大西洋各州]]，[[新泽西州|新泽西州]][[大西洋县|大西洋县]]的阿布西肯（{{lang|en|Absecon}}）记录到113毫米降雨量，[[纽约市|纽约市]]的[[中央公园_(纽约市)|中央公园]]附近则有99毫米，[[马萨诸塞州|马萨诸塞州]]的[[汤顿_(马萨诸塞州)|汤顿]]也有81毫米<ref name="hpcpa14" />。纽约州的[[五指湖|五指湖]]因风暴残留产生的暴雨引发洪灾，多条道路被冲毁<ref>{{cite report | author = | title = Tropical Storm Barry Event Report for New York | year = 2007 | publisher = National Climatic Data Center | accessdate = 2008-11-19}}</ref>。纽约州东南部还爆发了山洪，并有强烈的阵风引起零星的树木受损<ref>{{cite report | author = | title = Tropical Storm Barry Event Report for New York (2) | year = 2007 | publisher = National Climatic Data Center | accessdate = 2008-11-19}}</ref>。新泽西州东北部还出现了高涨的潮汐，导致轻微的沿海洪灾<ref>{{cite report | author = | title = Tropical Storm Barry Event Report for New Jersey | year = 2007 | publisher = National Climatic Data Center | accessdate = 2008-11-25}}</ref>。

